x indicates potential network/database latency issues.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"currencyservice-1 rrt_max increased from 5327 to 56392 with a change ratio of 1.1971.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Elevated rrt_max suggests processing delays or network congestion.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice rrt_max increased from 3336 to 43727 with a change ratio of 1.1949.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "trace_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\",\n    \"timeout\",\n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n    \"connection_refused\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Latency spikes occurred during requests from frontend to productcatalogservice.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Frontend calls to 'hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/GetProduct' show anomaly avg duration 13999.15 ms, which is a significant increase over the normal average duration 11480.30 ms.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Notable delays during 'POST /hipstershop.CartService/AddItem' events with evidence of cascading failures.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Latency spike from 5216.28 ms to 52457.33 ms between frontend and cartservice.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"Possible Redis bottleneck affecting cartservice functions.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Cartservice to redis interactions (e.g. HMSET) experienced anomaly avg duration 21699.33 ms versus normal duration 1655.44 ms.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Increased processing time in sending/shipping-related processes from checkoutservice.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Checkoutservice had a large time anomaly in GetQuote, increasing durations from 199.53 ms to 879.0 ms.\"\n    },\n    {\n 